      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior finish still holds a beautiful luster, with only minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well that is barely noticeable. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show light, natural creasing but remain supple with no rips or thinning. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound\u2014it starts promptly, idles smoothly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It has been serviced regularly, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. This is a dependable, high-quality car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 29500.0,
